-- Romanian Utility Apa Serv Seek Bids for Water System Upgrades
-- B y   I r i n a   S a v u
-- 2012-11-27T19:01:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-27/romanian-utility-apa-serv-seek-bids-for-water-system-upgrades.html
Apa Serv SA, a Romanian regional
utility, is seeking bids from companies interested in upgrading
the water and sewer system in the northeastern town of Targu
Neamt.  Apa Serv plans to award a contract estimated at 64 million
lei ($18 million), according to a European Union  procurement
document . Bids can be submitted until Jan. 21, it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Irina Savu in Bucharest at 
 isavu@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  